                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8590" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0564</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1931 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">筑梦云端，智启未来：神州数码集团关键岗位人才梯队的搭建之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Building Dreams and Enlightening the Future with Digital Intelligence: The Path of Transformation in Building the Talent Echelon of Key Positions in Digital China Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵宜萱，魏丹霞，龚先量，张佳蕾，赵曙明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">神州数码集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人才梯队；人才激活；数字化转型；神州数码集团；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">talent echelon; talent activation; digital transformation; Digital China</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例在介绍神州数码集团数字化转型战略的实施及人力资源管理数字化过程的基础上，描述了神州数码集团搭建关键岗位人才梯队时所面临的困境与挑战。这些困境主要集中在人岗错配、职业发展通道受限以及面向未来的人才储备方面，针对上述困境，神州数码集团采取了有效措施，如建立人才画像、建立动态的关键岗位监测系统、构建能力模型、采取多元的选拔与培养体系、实施轮岗制度及以价值创造为核心的考核激励体系、建立全生命周期的人才管理模式等，以此激活人才潜力、拓宽职业发展通道、做好人才储备。本案例希望通过神州数码集团的人才梯队搭建问题，启发学员思考数字化转型背景之下如何有效利用资源培养人才，激活人才潜力，建立企业与员工双赢的发展局面。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On the basis of introducing the implementation of the digital transformation strategy of Digital China Group and the digitization process of human resources management, this case describes the dilemma of building the talent echelon for key positions faced by Digital China Group, which mainly focuses on the talent allocation of new business positions, the limited career development channels and the plight of talent reserve facing the future, and then puts forward the effective measures taken by Digital China, such as establishing a talent profile and a dynamic key position monitoring system, building a capability model, adopting the diversified selection and training system, rotation system, the implementation of value creation as the core assessment and incentive system, the establishment of a full life cycle talent management model, so as to activate talent potential, broaden career development channels, and make talent reserves for the future. Through the construction of the talent echelon of Digital China Group, this case hopes to inspire students to think about how to effectively use resources to train talents and activate talent potential against the backdrop of the digital transformation, so as to establish a win-win situation for both enterprises and employees.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源基础观；个人-环境匹配理论；人力资源管理价值链模型；战略人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
